Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點熟悉起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是匹很溫順的馬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人照顧它就足夠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
