Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnArial}Andaré por esa luz\N{\r}我將會走在那光芒上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 請別妨礙我們好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才也是明明在選拔的說卻凈做些多餘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還算開心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是專業的 不如說你們應該感謝我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,專業？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樂隊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實還有一個人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnArial}Muchacha!!!\N{\r}女孩!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有大賣的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 年輕人大概不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Condor Queens
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}廣告裡也出現過喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Condor Queens？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人豎起一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Co Co Co Condor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Co Co Condor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別比劃了 怪難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在低調地全國巡演中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音樂已經不只是工作而是人生的一部份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----鳥語-----
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Condor Queens？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是爺爺的主打曲目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------------------------
