Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs74\c&H000000&\blur2\shad5\3c&HB8B8C4&\fad(640,0)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\b0\i1\4c&H606060&\pos(581,469)}舞動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我追那輛自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟蹤狂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟蹤狂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小時候起一直是你們的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 請參加World Music Festival好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那來夏醬你們的選拔就算輸了可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為不可能贏的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不挑舞臺主義的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那活動之前去紗羽家住怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！等等啊來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空房間的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽家是寺廟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在寺廟裡什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是什麼佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱沒在缺錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有住習慣的自己的「家」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寺廟裡有沒有寬敞的停車場呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停車場？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是媽媽的熟人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我實在是太高興了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnArial}Hoy hace un buen día\N{\r}今天是一個好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 合唱的排練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天說是中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個什麼樂隊一起去沖田家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不錯的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒這麼悠閒自在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話 日本實在是太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那需要什麼就儘管說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝您的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也一起來怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就不客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 紗羽 今天讓我住下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好好的和他們說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就和他們一起睡在野營車裡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碗小？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amigo 我找到了喲
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真昼的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你能找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快請坐 快請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我馬上就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是開路邊演唱會的時期跟真昼相遇的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起寫了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AMIGO AMIGO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這是我們唯一的熱賣歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那首歌與其說是創作的 倒不如說是誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有聽真昼提起過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 從媽媽那裡沒聽過什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們來說她是很特別的朋友 也是恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至可能是戀人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 我們可不是你爸爸喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別跟小姑娘開沒品的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那時候的真昼真像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真昼更爽朗點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭髮也更長一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恍如昨日吶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真昼竟然已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薩布萊 稍微跑幾步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小心點哦 我家的寶安姆不是在害怕麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寶安姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 寶安姆 要被吃掉了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會吃呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 我是想說今天合唱部的排練事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天沒有打工 不是在學校練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以缺席嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午後在海邊小屋的舞臺上他們要演奏一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,專業人員 說不定能學到點什麼的說...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 不如停止練習大家都一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還什麼都沒有做不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是玩玩的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算對手是我所敬仰的強大騎手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起賽馬的話我也絕不想輸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏如果不親自去唱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅在粉絲俱樂部尋求滿足的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要退出合唱部了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！蠢貨！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有假音的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始補習咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職業的話 現場是絕對不能遲到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊小屋的舞臺 想讓我們讓給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是高中三年級了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算畢業了 也還是能繼續歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這和現在不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:12:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的成員 現在的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的歌 只有現在才能唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我們讓給你麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 唉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 你們的畢業典禮什麼的我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊可是都快人生畢業典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可沒老糊塗到把所愛之物讓給別人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 Amigo 回到屬於你的舞臺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志保姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好正好 給 衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽的話現在不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 稍微有點想問的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有能讓我們演出的舞臺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有假音的感覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假音？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個的說...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼宮本不來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我們的話 只能練腹肌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為她會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了 坂井呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她理論上來說也是合唱部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是原音樂科的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來還一次都沒聽她唱過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,補習的時候來了哦 下次邀請她下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 很棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微讓我也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 正好有一家還沒有聯繫說決定人選的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 雖然不知道會不會被採用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去試試
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的...母子倆一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界音樂舞臺的歌手已經決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 正好就在剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個熟人對這個有興趣 說是能幫忙介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似還在這附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 能找到舞臺真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好久沒全力跑過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮本同學 答案找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是天才多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話現在肯定已經
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然一個人唱不了歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學 放棄音樂是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我也不是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮本同學 知道這首歌的事情麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我來夏就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個 其實不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是首好歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學 多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我和奏就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果宮本還是沒有來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家各自抽時間聽一下CD
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習好自己的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起練習的時間已經沒多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是你田中！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,參加獎什麼的我們不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獲取人氣投票的優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登上主演的舞台唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----鳥語-----
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}亂七八糟的啊...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}為啥？...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配合一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（-----鳥語-----）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----鳥語-----
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那邊沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊很遠啦誰都不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拿個參加獎的好像...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊氣氛好熱烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這首歌是...和奏的媽媽參與創作的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的舞台沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒聚集起什麼人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有人聚集才演唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是唱歌去吸引人群聚集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追加曲目時要一起來舞臺上唱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必勞煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我們有自己的舞台啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很小是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的就這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們自己來唱就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去我們的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你放棄音樂了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些充實的時光 荒廢的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悅的時光 傷感的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所想創作的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣的歌曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然那時我們並不理解這些話的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像夢話一樣笑了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那個說的可能就是現在的你呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄不了音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是放棄不放棄的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音樂這東西無時無刻不與你同在啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnArial}Personal del corazón también es música\N{\r}人的心跳亦是音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前曾被真昼這麼說過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄不了音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追加曲目請準備開始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在你出生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真昼交給我們的信函
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能拿著它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望以後能有時間再慢慢聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是沒人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有的嘛 三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請認真地唱唱看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺有個很不可愛的傢伙在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟來夏很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問可以合影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍照謝絕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂會被抽掉的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 和奏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 和奏的蛋糕也買了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不可以放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾身即為馬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊這異想天開的白日夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}第五話 捨棄 無法捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.19,0:23:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房間裡的鋼琴 想要收起來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OPJ-------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.50,0:00:39.00,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}胸の奥が高鳴る
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.47,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}熱い声に気付いたら
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.51,0:00:44.72,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}スタートラインは
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.72,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}君の目の前にある
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.97,0:00:50.35,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}まだ見えない道でも
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.10,0:00:53.85,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}走り始めればいいさ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.06,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}諦めるよりも
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.73,0:00:59.19,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}素敵だと思わない？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.48,0:01:04.28,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}いつも不安はすぐ傍で
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.32,0:01:10.20,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}駆け出す思いを 締め付けるけれど
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.33,0:01:13.50,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}今を越えて 歩き出す
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.54,0:01:16.25,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}未知なる道に光を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.29,0:01:19.21,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}初めてを 繰り返し
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.84,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}掴み取れ 明日を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.88,0:01:24.97,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}さっさと友達が無限の
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.01,0:01:27.64,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}夢抱きしめ 進むのさ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.72,0:01:33.56,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}輝いてる自分を信じていい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.35,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}立ち上がる力に
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.44,0:01:39.19,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}盛大の愛を込めて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.94,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}思うまま 旅立とう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.98,0:01:47.95,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}新しい世界の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OPC-------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.50,0:00:39.00,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}胸口傳出響亮的聲響
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.47,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}希望有誰能夠注意到這熱忱的聲音
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.51,0:00:44.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}人生的Start Line
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}無時無刻都會出現在你的眼前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.97,0:00:50.35,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}即使是看不到盡頭的道路
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.10,0:00:53.85,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}只要踏出第一步就是前進
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.06,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}比起直接放棄
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.73,0:00:59.19,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不覺得這樣更好嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.48,0:01:04.28,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不安總是徘徊在我們的身旁
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.32,0:01:10.20,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}將這份鼓動的心情 關閉在深處的抽屜裡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.33,0:01:13.50,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}讓我們邁出腳步越過現在
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.54,0:01:16.25,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}照亮那條未知的道路
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.29,0:01:19.21,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不斷重複著將終點轉變為起點
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.84,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}用我們的雙手抓住未來
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.88,0:01:24.97,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}趕快集結起夥伴
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.01,0:01:27.64,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}擁抱無限的夢想 向前推進
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.72,0:01:33.56,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}鼓起勇氣相信閃耀著的自己吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.35,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}將盛大的愛灌注進乾涸的心靈
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.44,0:01:39.19,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}給再次站起來的力量
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.94,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}就讓我們任著性子去旅行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.98,0:01:47.95,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}讓我們換乘進入新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------EDJ-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:23.23,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}晴れた日 雨の日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:30.24,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}皆がいればいつも 笑顔になれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:39.50,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}記憶の彼方まで 思い出したり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:43.67,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}揺蕩う声 耳澄まそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.97,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}さぁ 手を差し伸べられて輪の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:53.64,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}一人じゃない空間で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:57.94,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}夢中になってる時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:03.86,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}心地良い風が吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:11.03,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}笑ったり 泣いたり 歌ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:16.62,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}閉じていたこころも開いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:23.46,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}思い出のフレーズ 口ずさむ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.84,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}奏でよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------EDC-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:23.23,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}無論是放晴的日子 還是下雨的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:30.24,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}有大家陪伴在身邊的話 無論何時都能保持笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:39.50,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}即使在記憶的最深處 也要回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:43.67,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}這搖蕩的聲音 讓我們傾耳聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:48.01,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}來嘛 讓我們一起伸出雙手鏈接起圓環
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:53.64,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}製造出不是一個人的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:57.94,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}享受著這夢幻般的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:03.86,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}一股清風吹起平靜了心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:11.03,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}歡笑了 哭泣了 勇敢的歌唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:16.62,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}曾經緊閉著的心房也悄然敞開了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:23.46,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}充滿回憶的旋律 輕聲吟唱著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:28.84,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}奏響吧
