Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:46.15,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}波に思い馳せって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:46.15,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}隨著波濤浮想聯翩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.24,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}見えるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.24,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}能看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:53.22,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}あの白い砂浜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:53.22,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}那純白的沙灘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.70,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}熱い太陽の下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.70,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}和炎炎烈日下
